			<dialogue>77,周瑜:如果老天能够再给我一点时间，我根本不会与孔明联手的……</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>19,4,77</storyAction>
