			<storyAction>0,4,21</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:还有两个在西方。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,20</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,荀彧:我看应该在蜀国领地内。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,20</storyAction>
